Has
Few mistakes:
1. Moving the email out of the Customer relation is incorrect / Unnecesary unless you plan for multiple emails per customer
2. Product names tend to not be unique, so Name, Price and Stock can all be kept inside Product relation.
3. Order relation is not even in 1st normal form, unless I plan to have each order include only one type of product (Which is not the case). I completely missed this.
